edits. This isn't exactly the kind of film I would expect to see an Etch A Sketch in, but I am absolutely honored to pursue all-new frontier in my ridiculously niche choice of medium. It's incredible to realize that (as far as my research has shown), I am the very first Etch A Sketch artist to have their art in a bona fide movie!</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/OPwgxul</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[pikajane]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>The next time you hear it ...</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/xJXGozv</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/GTPVQzw.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/xJXGozv</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[blank666man]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>point</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/duVfOWm</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/fk7SBbC.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/duVfOWm</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[PiercedViking]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Wait, what?</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/nuHbTKu</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/F8n7JoJ.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/nuHbTKu</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[vidadobl6]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Like a prayer.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/V6ZISZ5</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Hn61tGO.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/V6ZISZ5</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[sleeperkid]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Cool Project</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/bXw5nkU</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Gfhnhbe.jpg" style="max-wid